cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it focuses on machine reading comprehension. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a model based on neural networks. The paper also mentions the use of convolutional and recurrent neural networks, which suggests it may belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as well.
